    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118450/extras/9abcb7a661ed49c4373b3bed5bb36ee0.avif?t=1752425231\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到可爱卡通猫的精彩世界！准备好迎接一场激动人心的“找不同”冒险吧，这里有42个充满挑战的关卡等待着你。每个关卡包含两张相似的图片，你需要找出其中的六个差异。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是什么让这款游戏特别？每只猫咪都有独特的职业或爱好，从医生和工程师到摇滚音乐家和博主，应有尽有。你会喜欢上简单又可爱的画面以及动听的背景音乐，它们会让你完全沉浸在游戏的氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏适合大人和小孩，是打发时间的好选择。沉浸在专业猫咪的迷人世界中，提升你的观察力和专注力吧！现在就购买游戏，进入“Cast Cats”的精彩世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >42个关卡 + 1个隐藏关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超多猫咪！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >悦耳的音乐伴奏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松的游戏玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >适合儿童和成人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不处罚错误，无时间限制，随心所欲地玩</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118450/extras/ff0cc3d48aeea7bb12aef7d4264d2d8d.poster.avif?t=1752425231\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118450/extras/ff0cc3d48aeea7bb12aef7d4264d2d8d.webm?t=1752425231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118450/extras/ff0cc3d48aeea7bb12aef7d4264d2d8d.mp4?t=1752425231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
